# 🛠 String Methods Revised

| Method | Use |
|---------|-----|
| `upper()` | Converts all characters to uppercase |
| `lower()` | Converts all characters to lowercase |
| `capitalize()` | Capitalizes the first character |
| `title()` | Capitalizes the first letter of every word |
| `swapcase()` | Swaps uppercase and lowercase letters |
| `strip()` | Removes leading and trailing spaces |
| `lstrip()` | Removes leading spaces |
| `rstrip()` | Removes trailing spaces |
| `replace()` | Replaces one substring with another |
| `split()` | Splits a string into a list |
| `join()` | Joins iterable elements into a string |
| `find()` | Returns the first occurrence index |
| `rfind()` | Returns the last occurrence index |
| `index()` | Returns the index of a substring |
| `count()` | Counts occurrences of a substring |
| `startswith()` | Checks if the string starts with a substring |
| `endswith()` | Checks if the string ends with a substring |
| `isalpha()` | Checks whether all characters are alphabets |
| `isdigit()` | Checks whether all characters are digits |
| `isalnum()` | Checks whether all characters are alphanumeric |
| `islower()` | Checks if all letters are lowercase |
| `isupper()` | Checks if all letters are uppercase |
| `isspace()` | Checks if all characters are whitespace |
| `center()` | Centers the string with specified width |
| `zfill()` | Pads zeros to the left of the string |

